ow";s:15:"ABOUT FRANKIE''S";s:5:"title";s:81:"A neighborhood breakfast burrito spot with enough craft to feel worth the detour.";s:10:"paragraphs";a:2:{i:0;s:65:"Use this section to tell the brand story in two short paragraphs.";i:1;s:58:"Keep the copy specific, local, and operationally credible.";}s:5:"image";s:93:"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/item-1600000000102810433_1759808489.jpg.jpeg";s:5:"facts";a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:"value";s:10:"Open daily";s:5:"label";s:12:"8 AM to 3 PM";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:"value";s:12:"Agoura Hills";s:5:"label";s:21:"Roadside Drive pickup";}}}s:5:"proof";a:5:{s:7:"eyebrow";s:12:"SOCIAL PROOF";s:5:"title";s:64:"Trust cues that reassure people before they commit to breakfast.";s:4:"body";s:89:"Testimonials are managed as their own content type so they can be reviewed independently.";s:15:"backgroundImage";s:58:"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/home.jpeg";s:5:"items";a:6:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:4:"Ajay";s:4:"body";s:162:"Absolutely loved the food! The burritos are packed with flavor and feel super fresh. You can really tell they care about quality. Definitely my go-to spot now!”";s:6:"source";s:0:"";}i:1;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:5:"rahul";s:4:"body";s:47:"the food is awesome and cool. love the burritos";s:6:"source";s:0:"";}i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:10:"jayantilal";s:4:"body";s:47:"the food is awesome and cool. love the burritos";s:6:"source";s:0:"";}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:7:"Emma K.";s:4:"body";s:171:"I didn’t think a breakfast burrito could taste this good. Everything is fresh, perfectly seasoned, and wrapped just right. Frankie’s is my new go-to spot every weekend";s:6:"source";s:0:"";}i:4;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:7:"Jason M";s:4:"body";s:175:"Frankie’s Breakfast Burrito completely changed my mornings. The flavors are insane, the portions are huge, and it actually keeps me full till lunch. I’m officially hooked!";s:6:"source";s:0:"";}i:5;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"mark specter";s:4:"body";s:98:""The flavors are simple, pure, and ba